window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Matti Puletasi finally has the name of one of the people responsible for her parents’ kidnapping. He’s a powerful billionaire with magical security strong enough to keep out dragons, but she’s determined to get in to question him. Make that interrogate him.</p> <p>Sarrlevi, the elf assassin she’s fallen in love with, would usually help her, but he’s fighting a battle of his own. The wounds he received in their last skirmish aren’t healing, and something in his blood is affecting his mind. And it’s getting worse.</p> <p>If Matti can’t reach the billionaire and find a way to heal Sarrlevi, she could lose everyone she loves.</p>"; 
